query:
SELECT q.id, q.sectionId, q.questionNumber, q.questionText, q.exampleEvidence, s.name as sectionName, s.type
FROM complianceQuestions q
JOIN complianceSections s ON q.sectionId = s.id
WHERE s.type = 'serviceUser'
ORDER BY q.sectionId, CAST(SUBSTRING_INDEX(q.questionNumber, '.', -1) AS UNSIGNED)
LIMIT 5;
